{# Synthesizes classify-threat findings with CWE/OWASP/ATLAS taxonomy #}
{# Proposes RR-NNNN.yaml entries with surface: runtime #}
{# Emits reg.runtime.regulate Regulation span (P9) #}
{# Emits reg.regulation for downstream regulation action #}
